column2: SELECT d.dr7ObjID, s.plate, s.fiberid, s.mjd, s.ra, s.dec, s.z, gs.D4#_N_SUB, gs.D4#_N_SUB_ERR, gs.LICK_HD_A_SUB, gl.H_ALPHA_FLUX, gl.H_ALPHA_FLUX_ERR, gl.H_BETA_FLUX, gl.H_BETA_FLUX_ERR, gl.OIII_#_FLUX, gl.OIII_#_FLUX_ERR, gl.NII_#_FLUX, gl.OI_#_FLUX, gl.OI_#_FLUX_ERR, gl.NII_#_FLUX_ERR, #* (ws.w2mpro+#- (ws.w3mpro+#) ), ge.lgm_tot_p5#, ge.sfr_tot_p5#, ge.lgm_fib_p5#, ge.sfr_fib_p5#, gi.sn_median, gl.sigma_balmer, gl.H_ALPHA_EQW, ph.expAB_r, ph.deVAB_r, ph.petroR5#_r, ph.petroR9#_r, gs.lick_mgb_sub, gi.v_disp, gi.v_disp_err, ph.modelMag_g, ph.modelMag_r, ge.bptclass, ph.fiberMag_g, ph.fiberMag_r, ph.fiber2Mag_g, ph.fiber2Mag_r from SpecObj as s into mydb.sdss_dr1#_sample JOIN photoobjall as ph on s.bestObjID = ph.objID JOIN galSpecIndx as gs on s.specObjID = gs.specObjID JOIN galSpecInfo as gi on s.specObjID = gi.specObjID JOIN galSpecLine as gl on s.specObjID = gl.specObjID JOIN galSpecExtra as ge on s.specObjID = ge.specObjID JOIN wISE_xmatch as wg on s.bestObjID = wg.sdss_objid JOIN wISE_allsky as ws on ws.cntr = wg.wise_cntr INNER JOIN specDR7 as d on d.specObjID = s.specObjID WHERE s.z BETWEEN # AND #
